íŸ@d0c707c0c0ef3d02276f7118afade13cf2e9cd1d341de652fca7e3918dacb594ŸœTitle: title: export
Path: Examples
Content:
Export a definition from a module.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> module utils { export def my-command [] { "hello" } }; use utils my-command; my-command
hello

```
